Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:35.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士们，先生们，晚上好。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:46.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,La mort n'est jamais qu'un salut,ainsi mon ami a t'il murmurer jadis amon intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:42.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「死不过是解脱」我的朋友曾这样对我说。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:51.60,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,asupposer que la mort soit un salut,que veux tu donner quand atoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「若死是解脱，那你究竟想带给他们什么呢？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:52.90,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,mon ami arépondu en un souffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.40,0:01:50.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友只回答了一句话。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:58.00,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;50;70;20,Chez eux une souffrance et un remord éternel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:55.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我要给他们永远的痛苦与悔恨…」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我不会再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十二幕\N反击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的选择真的是正确吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就没什么真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓真理是在自己的信念之下创造出来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使同室操戈 甚至抛弃父母也在所不惜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不能光看父母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而要看眼前的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在弗朗兹死去的前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我听了您的告白后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就一直走到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着波光粼漓的河流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪就止不住地涌了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我还清楚地记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹给我留下了几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「绝对不要恨任何人」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「爱人的心情和恨人的心情」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「最初都是由思念之情中产生的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一切都告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为爱德蒙最后的单身之夜干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受莫尔塞夫将军之命前来迎接您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军即将进入巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将建立临时政府
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天之内莫尔塞夫大统领即将诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请带我去 到他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…费尔南·蒙代戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国民议会被我们东方宇宙军占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是重大的叛逆行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不承认 决不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…真无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您慎重发言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在解散原议会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣布巴黎进入戒严状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个名叫爱德蒙·唐泰斯的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 直到那天我还对人毫无戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心祈祷着父亲与未婚妻的幸福 渡过每日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现将你作为暗杀王子案的重大嫌疑人逮捕归案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙 爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被告发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人告密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据那封告发信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你持有记载暗杀王子案真相的信件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长去世前 应该交托给你一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按照船长的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备把信送到收件人那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「巴黎 鸡鹭街13号」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「诺瓦蒂埃先生」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信中写有与暗杀王子案有关的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中也包括维尔福的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不知情的我将信交给了当事人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你只是出色地完成了任务而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐泰斯先生 关于此信的事就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就会被释放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 维尔福先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知该如何感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未婚妻一定正焦急地等着我回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这封信的事你和别人说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 根据船长的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直坚守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道这封信的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到现在还相信王子是被敌人暗杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是地球方面的设计
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战争中牟取暴利的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望战争继续
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以暗杀为最坏结局收场 和平无望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中他们下怀 纷争扩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以暗杀的报复为名 战争愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然…然后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个不幸的男人…被埋葬于黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用了我的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在经济司法等界各自崭露头角
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在军事界爬到顶峰的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终向大统领的地位进发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫维尔福先生来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底犯了什么罪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没做 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆在被收监入伊夫堡的我面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无尽的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了对付边境外未知敌人的自动化要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也成了那控制系统的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 甚至连死亡的选择也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无限的地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不期望救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这身体消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那些夺去我一切 把我逼向毁灭的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:10:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都受到最残酷 最悲惨的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要给他们生不如死 永无止境的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.80,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:22.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:30.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:30.60,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon ami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}l'espoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le chagrin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.80,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le désir ardent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la résignation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:40.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:40.90,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la colère...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la terreur...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.20,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}le désespoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再一次希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}et anouveau l'espoir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等待着像你这样的人的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.00,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}cela fait des milliers d'années que j'attendais
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了借用这个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.50,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}al'intérieur de ce coprs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.00,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数千年间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.00,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}la venue de quelqu'un
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直等待着…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.80,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}comme...toi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:03.30,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.10,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Je suis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将与你同在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.40,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}avec toi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.60,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.60,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Et tu es
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也与我同在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}avec moi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借给你我的智慧和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.70,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Je te donne ma sagesse et mon pouvoir
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.20,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.20,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}et toi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.50,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要献出你的身体与心灵…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.50,notec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}tu m'offres ton esprit et ton corps...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 我是命运的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不过是这坚定的复仇之心在驱动着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是不希望您去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您打消这个念头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够命令基督山伯爵的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有基督山伯爵一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的心中 难道已经…没有任何人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所认识的伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道已经…已经消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙军正向大学等机关移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请市民们尽快避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙军正向大学等机关移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请市民们尽快避难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的金子 我的金子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间不过如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死刑 死刑 死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 别阻拦我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别关机哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对伯爵要保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器储藏库
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我不知道的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们见识一下我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯旋门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无能之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 巴黎终于被我征服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不应该是你所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尔南
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我说的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满溢着更多希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 这是国民所必需的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尔南
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是大统领夫人了 梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无所畏惧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙就活在我们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是你的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是我未婚夫的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以基督山伯爵的身份回到了我们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了复仇而回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇？你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和爱德蒙不是好友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么爱德蒙一定要向你复仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他…是好友…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从不认为那家伙是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你的漂亮话有多伤人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄出让他被捕的信的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他将会是钢铁之舰法老号的船长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我只是个马塞港的苦力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…是你的漂亮话让爱德蒙坠入不幸的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我对你说了多么过分的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开巴黎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经厌烦那种丧家犬般的人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够只能望其项背的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要留在这
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留在 我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记和你度过的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 费尔南
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔塞苔丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深爱着她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我爱你…胜过一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙还活着
