Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙代戈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那家伙还活着 我也不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基督山伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你对我做的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要夺走你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将继续祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为父亲 为母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有为最重要的您之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 岩窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十三幕\N爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然后期待
